prompts.frontCover:
A whimsical and charming beach scene illustrated in a flat 2D botanical style. The setting is a beautiful, serene beach with soft, sandy-colored shores and gentle teal-blue waves. Instead of regular palm trees, the scene features fantastical "Boba Palm Trees" with lush green fronds, but instead of coconuts, they are laden with clusters of large, glossy black tapioca pearls. A few of these boba pearls have fallen onto the sand. A charming cartoon-style illustration of the couple sits together on a beach blanket. They are laughing and clinking oversized, whimsical boba tea cups together in a toast. The entire scene is framed with light, elegant botanical elements like monstera leaves and tropical flowers in soft pastel colors, creating a beautiful, natural border. The overall style is painterly and slightly textured, with a warm, sunny color palette.

In the center, written in a beautiful, elegant, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"
